item.description:
MultiPay allows you to create a single payment transaction with multiple recipients.
Tap to add a recipient (&ldquo;Add&rdquo;) Finish and send the transaction (&ldquo;Send&rdquo;) Add a recipient After tapping the button &ldquo;+&rdquo;
Adding a new recipient is done using the same entry form as a single recipient payment.
See Send Coins.
Remove Recipients Swipe the Recipient row left/right off the screen to discard it.
Send After pressing the button &ldquo;Send&rdquo;
